WEBVTT

01:37.070 --> 01:40.940
[The Best Thing]

01:41.400 --> 01:45.870
[Episode 13: Ginger;
Pungent, slightly warm, relieves exterior cold, warms the stomach to stop vomiting, dissolves phlegm to ease coughing, and counteracts fish and crab toxins]

01:46.509 --> 01:47.640
Previously, I...

01:47.870 --> 01:50.039
I felt it wasn't the right time yet,

01:50.310 --> 01:51.870
so I didn't tell you explicitly.

01:52.870 --> 01:54.840
There were also too many people last night.

01:54.840 --> 01:56.039
I was afraid you'd be embarrassed

01:56.060 --> 01:57.620
so didn't express myself clearly either.

01:59.200 --> 02:00.040
But,

02:00.880 --> 02:02.640
I can say it again more formally.

02:11.430 --> 02:12.270
Shen Xifan,

02:14.380 --> 02:15.660
I like you.

02:30.000 --> 02:30.760
I'm sorry.

02:38.630 --> 02:41.030
I don't have any plans to be in a relationship right now.

02:41.360 --> 02:42.910
So, I'm sorry.

02:59.590 --> 03:00.310
Wait.

03:02.180 --> 03:04.780
I thought we were getting along well.

03:06.430 --> 03:08.590
I'm about to study abroad.

03:09.120 --> 03:09.910
I've said before,

03:10.400 --> 03:12.140
I don't plan to be in a relationship before going abroad.

03:12.160 --> 03:13.960
It's fine. While you study abroad, I can stay here...

03:13.960 --> 03:15.170
I might have given you the wrong impression.

03:23.890 --> 03:24.920
I'm sorry.

03:34.710 --> 03:35.150
Mis...

03:35.560 --> 03:36.400
Misunderstanding?

03:47.010 --> 03:49.170
Thank you for liking me.

04:00.830 --> 04:01.830
I'm sorry.

04:38.830 --> 04:39.590
Is this...

04:42.820 --> 04:44.260
your final decision?

04:57.680 --> 04:58.430
Alright.

05:02.750 --> 05:03.510
Okay.

05:08.750 --> 05:10.120
I've refilled your medicine for you.

05:11.870 --> 05:13.000
The hangover medicine.

05:13.610 --> 05:14.610
Remember to boil it before drinking.

05:25.720 --> 05:26.790
Remember to take your medicine on time.

05:56.590 --> 06:03.520
♫We are thousands of miles apart, in different cities♫

06:03.550 --> 06:10.310
♫Yet I linger, unwilling to leave, pretending you're here♫

06:10.450 --> 06:13.560
♫When you're away♫

06:17.700 --> 06:24.210
♫When you're away♫

06:27.950 --> 06:28.800
You're back.

06:30.870 --> 06:31.680
Yeah.

06:32.600 --> 06:33.480
What are you carrying?

06:33.480 --> 06:34.360
It's such a big bag.

06:36.950 --> 06:38.040
Is it Chinese medicine?

06:39.920 --> 06:41.510
I was saying, you were in such a hurry earlier.

06:41.510 --> 06:43.120
You went out with your hair still wet.

06:43.120 --> 06:44.190
Did you go to see He?

06:44.680 --> 06:45.430
He?

06:46.390 --> 06:47.600
Dr. He.

06:48.630 --> 06:49.270
Ms. Shen.

06:50.600 --> 06:52.630
Did Dr. He prescribed you Chinese medicine again?

06:53.650 --> 06:56.400
You should have invited him to come over to our place.

06:56.430 --> 06:57.950
Yeah, to have a meal.

06:58.240 --> 06:59.680
Yesterday at the gathering,

06:59.680 --> 07:01.190
you were drinking with Dr. He.

07:01.490 --> 07:03.000
He was the one who sent you back.

07:05.090 --> 07:07.530
I suppose he did send me back.

07:11.190 --> 07:12.240
Dr. He

07:12.240 --> 07:13.630
is so handsome.

07:13.950 --> 07:16.230
If I knew, why would I set up those blind dates for you?

07:17.270 --> 07:19.310
Dr. He looks so gentle and polite.

07:19.510 --> 07:21.630
He must like soft-spoken

07:21.630 --> 07:23.240
and elegant girls.

07:24.010 --> 07:25.600
Don't drink in front of him anymore.

07:29.400 --> 07:30.960
What stage are you two at now?

07:31.750 --> 07:33.870
What do you mean by "what stage"?

07:34.159 --> 07:35.750
You know, what stage of the relationship?

07:36.159 --> 07:37.920
We don't have any stage.

07:39.040 --> 07:40.270
Last night, when Dr. He

07:40.270 --> 07:41.560
sent you back,

07:41.560 --> 07:43.390
I could feel he has feelings for you.

07:43.950 --> 07:45.460
He took such good care of you.

07:59.240 --> 08:00.750
I turned him down.

08:02.510 --> 08:03.600
Why?

08:04.750 --> 08:06.510
Because I'm going to study abroad.

08:06.510 --> 08:08.520
I don't want to be in a relationship before I go study abroad.

08:08.540 --> 08:10.310
It's not even certain if you can go yet.

08:10.310 --> 08:12.070
Besides, it doesn't matter if you go abroad.

08:12.070 --> 08:14.000
You know, long-distance relationships, online relationships,

08:14.000 --> 08:15.070
and all kinds of relationships are possible now.

08:15.070 --> 08:16.830
Relationships and studying abroad are two separate things.

08:16.830 --> 08:17.800
They don't interfere with each other.

08:18.070 --> 08:19.000
They do interfere.

08:19.340 --> 08:21.630
I've already been through a long-distance relationship before.

08:21.870 --> 08:22.870
Before I go abroad,

08:24.420 --> 08:25.890
I don't want to be in a relationship.

08:39.460 --> 08:40.940
I've refilled your medication for you.

08:42.539 --> 08:43.700
The hangover medicine.

08:44.400 --> 08:45.680
Remember to boil it before drinking.

08:48.390 --> 08:49.440
Remember to take your medicine on time.

09:06.250 --> 09:07.290
I heard that

09:07.650 --> 09:09.370
during dinner on Friday,

09:09.390 --> 09:11.070
that handsome TCM doctor confessed his feelings to you.

09:14.320 --> 09:15.270
He said you drank too much,

09:15.270 --> 09:16.840
so that handsome TCM doctor even sent you home.

09:17.120 --> 09:18.720
So, what happened afterwards?

09:20.960 --> 09:23.130
Didn't he tell you that

09:23.290 --> 09:24.900
I turned down Dr. He?

09:26.000 --> 09:26.840
Why?

09:29.240 --> 09:31.910
Because before I go abroad to study,

09:32.110 --> 09:34.030
I don't plan to be in a relationship in the first place.

09:34.550 --> 09:37.270
So when he confessed to me,

09:38.360 --> 09:39.360
I rejected him.

09:45.940 --> 09:47.610
I'm already 27 years old.

09:48.120 --> 09:49.720
Before making any decision,

09:50.120 --> 09:51.960
I should be a bit more rational.

09:52.360 --> 09:53.430
Moreover,

09:53.450 --> 09:54.660
it's been proven

09:55.110 --> 09:56.790
that I really can't handle a long-distance relationship.

09:57.150 --> 09:58.920
Just like what happened with Yan Heng before.

09:59.600 --> 10:02.010
I'm afraid that one day he might regret it

10:02.240 --> 10:03.510
and realize

10:03.910 --> 10:05.630
that I'm not as good as he imagined.

10:27.270 --> 10:28.390
There's no major issues.

10:28.730 --> 10:30.850
Just the format of the table of contents could be optimized a bit more.

10:31.320 --> 10:32.240
Thank you, Senior He.

10:57.390 --> 10:58.120
What's wrong?

10:58.670 --> 11:01.120
Manager Shen rejected Suye.

11:05.040 --> 11:05.920
It's true.

11:07.000 --> 11:09.150
I couldn't tell during the morning rounds.

11:12.150 --> 11:12.960
His confession got rejected,

11:12.960 --> 11:14.390
yet he still has to focus on work.

11:14.720 --> 11:16.670
If it were me, I wouldn't even be able to even eat.

11:19.610 --> 11:20.640
But

11:20.670 --> 11:22.790
why did Manager Shen reject Senior He?

11:23.270 --> 11:24.440
I don't know.

11:24.960 --> 11:25.550
A couple of days ago,

11:25.550 --> 11:27.670
I even saw Manager Shen at Senior He's place.

11:28.200 --> 11:28.960
I thought they

11:28.960 --> 11:30.520
were just a step away from getting together.

11:30.870 --> 11:31.710
Who knew

11:32.320 --> 11:34.510
things would take such a sudden turn for the worse?

11:35.840 --> 11:36.720
Let's eat.

11:39.500 --> 11:40.900
Then we won't disturb your meal.

11:40.930 --> 11:41.410
Alright.

11:42.120 --> 11:42.880
Thank you, Senior He.

11:53.090 --> 11:57.080
[Staff Canteen]

12:24.120 --> 12:25.390
Monday bubble tea special,

12:25.390 --> 12:26.080
buy one get one free.

12:26.080 --> 12:27.200
They gave me a cup of oolong tea for free.

12:27.300 --> 12:27.940
Thanks.

12:28.690 --> 12:30.690
That's perfect, I don't need to brew tea now.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.390
It smells good.

12:36.400 --> 12:37.190
How is it?

12:39.150 --> 12:39.870
It's actually quite good.

12:40.380 --> 12:41.340
What flavour did you get?

12:41.370 --> 12:44.560
Mine is brown sugar ginger milk tea.

12:45.630 --> 12:47.000
Brown sugar ginger milk tea?

12:49.120 --> 12:51.080
You girls all like to drink these

12:51.080 --> 12:52.750
so-called ginger-infused hot drinks, huh?

12:53.890 --> 12:55.440
The weather has been getting cooler lately,

12:55.550 --> 12:56.840
so I just wanted to drink something hot.

12:57.240 --> 13:00.000
Actually, whether there's ginger in it to ward off the cold

13:00.000 --> 13:01.070
isn't really that important.

13:01.240 --> 13:02.440
What we're drinking is the mood.

13:04.030 --> 13:04.870
The mood?

13:08.000 --> 13:09.200
To put it bluntly,

13:09.200 --> 13:10.550
we need the sugar in the bubble tea

13:10.550 --> 13:12.200
to stimulate dopamine secretion in the brain

13:12.200 --> 13:13.550
to make ourselves feel a bit better.

13:15.600 --> 13:16.600
That's quite interesting.

13:17.170 --> 13:18.980
Drinking too much bubble tea can make you gain weight.

13:19.010 --> 13:20.840
When you want to lose weight, you'll be in a bad mood.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.030
But usually,

13:22.030 --> 13:23.320
you like to drink bubble tea

13:23.320 --> 13:24.670
to switch up your mood.

13:25.000 --> 13:25.870
Don't you find that contradictory?

13:27.240 --> 13:29.480
Now you can order bubble tea with sugar substitutes,

13:30.310 --> 13:31.470
so it's not that bad.

13:32.720 --> 13:34.410
Sugar substitutes are...

13:35.360 --> 13:36.510
They're considered

13:39.270 --> 13:40.670
a substitutionary satisfaction.

13:41.250 --> 13:43.250
It means you're not actually consuming sugar,

13:43.280 --> 13:45.280
but you get psychological satisfaction.

13:46.000 --> 13:48.310
And it tastes much better than sugar-free options.

13:50.450 --> 13:52.260
Substitutionary satisfaction.

14:01.200 --> 14:02.080
See.

14:03.390 --> 14:05.840
After repeated discussions and studies within the institute,

14:06.510 --> 14:08.400
we may have to suspend

14:08.480 --> 14:09.960
your research on breast cancer.

14:15.150 --> 14:16.150
I know.

14:17.510 --> 14:19.240
The project was initially approved,

14:19.680 --> 14:22.370
allowing you to lead students in research for a while, then suspended.

14:23.670 --> 14:25.590
It's a waste of your effort.

14:27.020 --> 14:28.830
I tried my best to advocate for you too,

14:29.840 --> 14:30.930
but there's nothing we can do.

14:32.630 --> 14:33.390
As you know,

14:34.390 --> 14:36.700
the institute's annual research funding is limited.

14:37.120 --> 14:38.920
The amount allocated to oncology is also limited.

14:39.600 --> 14:42.330
The institute certainly hopes that this funding

14:42.360 --> 14:43.610
can be used on projects

14:43.630 --> 14:45.710
that are more likely to yield results.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.270
I understand.

14:50.750 --> 14:52.280
For the past three years, you've been persisting

14:52.300 --> 14:53.700
in researching palliative care

14:54.900 --> 14:56.070
and I admire you for that.

14:57.120 --> 14:59.480
But this direction is indeed too niche

14:59.480 --> 15:01.390
and it's not easy to produce results.

15:04.740 --> 15:05.850
I hope you can

15:06.360 --> 15:07.720
understand the institute's decision.

15:09.250 --> 15:10.010
Next year.

15:10.880 --> 15:12.540
Next year, I will do my utmost

15:12.730 --> 15:14.060
to keep your research project.

15:17.630 --> 15:18.390
Alright.

15:18.870 --> 15:19.620
Thank you, Director.

15:21.630 --> 15:22.870
If there's nothing else,

15:22.870 --> 15:23.960
I'll head back to the outpatient clinic.

16:06.790 --> 16:08.270
Heat up the Chinese medicine yourself, okay?

16:10.430 --> 16:12.360
I'll drink it in a couple of days.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.730
Why won't you drink it?

16:13.760 --> 16:15.000
It's already been prescribed, hasn't it?

16:15.550 --> 16:17.240
That's He's heartfelt gesture.

16:20.420 --> 16:21.260
I get it.

16:28.440 --> 16:29.780
I want to go downstairs for a walk.

16:30.000 --> 16:32.200
After you two are done cleaning up, get some rest early.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.510
Come back early, okay?

16:33.940 --> 16:35.180
Be careful, it's cold out there.

16:35.910 --> 16:37.910
Don't worry, I'm heading down now.

17:15.400 --> 17:17.550
Why aren't you wearing socks in this cold weather?

17:19.619 --> 17:22.660
I was just planning to go downstairs for a stroll,

17:22.990 --> 17:24.609
so I forgot about it.

17:27.230 --> 17:27.950
Sure.

17:39.850 --> 17:41.090
I just got back from working overtime.

17:45.260 --> 17:45.680
So you...

17:45.680 --> 17:46.820
You must be tired from working overtime.

17:48.160 --> 17:50.540
Well, I'll head home now.

17:52.070 --> 17:52.790
Good night.

17:57.360 --> 18:03.200
♫I never wish to wake from my dream♫

18:04.040 --> 18:09.440
♫In the late autumn wind, I hold you close♫

18:10.890 --> 18:16.950
♫Longing will pass through the vast sea of people♫

18:17.820 --> 18:22.940
♫As long as you come, my waiting won’t be in vain♫

18:24.660 --> 18:30.250
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

18:31.470 --> 18:34.330
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

18:34.860 --> 18:38.330
♫Cherish the youth♫

18:40.180 --> 18:46.100
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

18:47.070 --> 18:53.550
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

18:55.540 --> 19:01.460
♫Missing you is the most beautiful poem in my life♫

19:01.190 --> 19:02.510
If you have ginger at home,

19:02.400 --> 19:07.610
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

19:02.890 --> 19:05.090
you can slice some and make ginger tea.

19:05.750 --> 19:06.750
Don't catch a cold.

21:17.070 --> 21:17.830
He Suye.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.160
He Suye.

21:21.070 --> 21:22.030
Driver, please open the door.

21:24.960 --> 21:26.240
He Suye.

21:28.480 --> 21:29.770
He Suye.

21:31.400 --> 21:32.670
He Suye.

21:39.490 --> 21:40.770
He Suye.

22:20.110 --> 22:20.830
Go ahead, tell me.

22:21.480 --> 22:23.070
Why are you so troubled?

22:26.830 --> 22:28.000
Not going to talk?

22:30.640 --> 22:31.920
It's up to you whether you want to talk or not.

22:32.590 --> 22:34.310
I can figure it out with a bit of calculation.

22:35.790 --> 22:38.200
Is it related to Miss Shen?

22:48.070 --> 22:49.400
I just feel that she...

22:50.190 --> 22:51.460
is a bit heartless.

22:54.750 --> 22:55.760
To be honest,

22:55.920 --> 22:57.870
I'm starting to doubt

22:58.160 --> 23:00.480
if I'm being too presumptuous.

23:07.510 --> 23:08.370
You know,

23:09.640 --> 23:12.160
you finally like a girl,

23:14.840 --> 23:16.600
but you can't force it.

23:18.000 --> 23:19.160
If it doesn't work out, let it go.

23:20.100 --> 23:21.930
After all, you're over thirty.

23:22.680 --> 23:24.170
Don't make things difficult for yourself.

23:25.900 --> 23:26.730
Do you understand?

23:30.480 --> 23:31.160
I understand.

23:43.440 --> 23:44.400
Let me pour you some more.

23:49.920 --> 23:54.890
[Manager of Front Office]

24:03.760 --> 24:04.820
The scent is gone.

24:25.000 --> 24:29.450
[Congratulations on your offer]

24:33.310 --> 24:35.310
It seems we still have to part ways.

24:37.950 --> 24:40.120
I made the right decision,

24:41.340 --> 24:42.100
didn't I?

25:20.070 --> 25:22.160
Drink this tangerine peel water before you go back.

25:23.310 --> 25:24.000
Why?

25:24.720 --> 25:27.850
You've been preoccupied with Miss Shen's matter

25:27.920 --> 25:29.070
qnd weren't focused on eating.

25:29.920 --> 25:31.190
I'm worried you might have indigestion.

25:31.280 --> 25:32.390
Drink some tangerine peel water.

25:33.200 --> 25:34.440
It helps with digestion and relieves stagnation.

26:35.550 --> 26:38.710
[Winter]

26:52.920 --> 26:55.070
Isn't this heater a bit too small?

26:55.070 --> 26:55.850
Will it be enough?

26:55.880 --> 26:57.710
Although this heater is relatively small,

26:57.730 --> 26:59.450
its effect is very good.

26:59.470 --> 27:01.280
It will definitely be warm enough for winter.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.270
Okay, let's plug it in then.

27:02.270 --> 27:03.510
Alright, shall we put it here?

27:13.240 --> 27:15.050
This was knocked off earlier while making the bedding.

27:17.190 --> 27:18.990
This is...

27:32.640 --> 27:34.240
When we were tidying up the room just now,

27:34.240 --> 27:35.480
we accidentally knocked it over.

27:35.480 --> 27:36.680
Where should it be placed?

27:36.930 --> 27:38.730
Give it to me, I'll eat it later.

27:40.750 --> 27:42.120
Since winter is approaching,

27:42.140 --> 27:44.490
we've changed your bedding to something warmer.

27:44.890 --> 27:46.130
It's humid in these mountains, isn't it?

27:46.270 --> 27:47.910
So we applied for a heater for you.

27:48.240 --> 27:49.550
If you need anything else,

27:49.550 --> 27:50.720
you can always come to me.

27:53.070 --> 27:55.390
Did you not rest well recently?

27:55.840 --> 27:58.510
You looked rosy just a few days ago,

27:58.940 --> 28:00.850
but today you seem a bit haggard.

28:01.270 --> 28:02.240
Is it because

28:02.640 --> 28:03.630
you're a bit tired?

28:07.440 --> 28:08.870
I've been having some insomnia.

28:10.000 --> 28:11.960
Then you must be having something on your mind.

28:13.410 --> 28:15.470
Come, come. Sit down and chat with me.

28:23.880 --> 28:25.480
I made a decision,

28:26.640 --> 28:28.000
but I'm not happy about it.

28:29.200 --> 28:30.270
I'm wondering

28:30.590 --> 28:32.460
if I made a mistake.

28:33.790 --> 28:35.310
In this world,

28:35.750 --> 28:38.550
there's no absolute right or wrong.

28:39.830 --> 28:41.590
It's only about whether you regret it or not.

28:43.550 --> 28:45.090
If you're having insomnia,

28:45.830 --> 28:48.640
could it be that you're feeling some regret?

28:50.110 --> 28:50.610
I...

28:50.680 --> 28:52.400
I shouldn't be regretting it, should I?

29:01.820 --> 29:05.140
Life is like the clouds in the sky.

29:06.830 --> 29:09.070
Gathering and parting are all destined.

29:13.480 --> 29:14.880
If it's meant to be,

29:15.710 --> 29:17.270
even if they turn into rain,

29:18.880 --> 29:19.880
they will

29:20.120 --> 29:21.940
fall into the same lake.

29:54.720 --> 29:56.070
Do you know how to play?

29:56.750 --> 29:57.590
It's lagging, it's lagging.

29:58.530 --> 29:59.690
I'm still better at this, right?

30:00.350 --> 30:01.240
How do I jump?

30:02.480 --> 30:03.400
Press this, press this.

30:11.830 --> 30:13.420
When are you coming back this year?

30:15.030 --> 30:16.310
I'm coming back tomorrow.

30:17.190 --> 30:18.190
Have you booked your flight?

30:18.750 --> 30:20.240
Yes, I'll arrive in the evening.

30:22.390 --> 30:23.870
Do you want me to send a car to pick you up?

30:23.890 --> 30:24.560
No need,

30:25.110 --> 30:26.270
I can take a taxi myself.

30:27.930 --> 30:28.650
By the way,

30:29.000 --> 30:31.330
Auntie Wang

30:31.390 --> 30:32.780
is also coming to spend the New Year with us.

30:33.880 --> 30:34.960
Just wanted to let you know.

30:36.600 --> 30:37.430
Okay.

30:40.300 --> 30:40.830
Hanging up now.

31:23.790 --> 31:25.200
I was just thinking

31:25.200 --> 31:27.550
that you rejected Dr. He too harshly.

31:28.190 --> 31:29.070
I didn't expect that

31:29.070 --> 31:30.240
you've already received the offer so soon.

31:33.030 --> 31:34.070
Have you told him?

31:34.510 --> 31:35.750
About receiving the offer.

31:45.200 --> 31:46.070
I know.

31:46.670 --> 31:48.750
It's not just because of the long-distance relationship between you two.

31:50.370 --> 31:51.610
Your previous relationship

31:51.640 --> 31:53.680
still casts a big shadow over you, doesn't it?

32:02.330 --> 32:03.640
But, Shen Xifan,

32:05.030 --> 32:06.550
finding someone who genuinely cares for you

32:06.550 --> 32:07.610
is not easy.

32:08.390 --> 32:09.550
Can you stop pushing him away

32:09.550 --> 32:11.050
over and over?

32:12.370 --> 32:14.650
It's like how I kept pushing and pulling with Lin Yishen.

32:14.980 --> 32:16.110
In the end, we missed our chance.

32:17.440 --> 32:18.750
Do you think we are

32:18.750 --> 32:20.240
still friends now?

32:32.960 --> 32:33.720
What are you doing?

32:33.790 --> 32:35.310
Li Jie just told me

32:35.310 --> 32:36.750
that he's at the handsome TCM doctor's place.

32:37.590 --> 32:38.510
We'll go there now.

32:38.510 --> 32:39.530
You need to clear things up with him.

32:40.790 --> 32:41.640
I don't want to.

32:41.960 --> 32:42.640
What should I

32:42.640 --> 32:43.340
even say?

32:43.370 --> 32:44.610
Say anything.

32:44.790 --> 32:46.720
At least tell him that you do care about him.

32:47.510 --> 32:49.740
Do you know what the most crucial part is?

32:50.360 --> 32:52.230
It's not that you didn't tell him about it,

32:52.640 --> 32:53.830
it's that he feels as if

32:53.830 --> 32:55.160
you don't care about his feelings at all.

32:55.590 --> 32:57.000
Even if you two are just platonic friends,

32:57.000 --> 32:58.550
you went through this matter together.

32:58.550 --> 33:00.480
You shouldn't exclude him completely, right?

33:08.790 --> 33:09.750
Where are you guys?

33:10.110 --> 33:11.310
We're at Suye's place.

33:11.720 --> 33:12.790
Can I come and join you?

33:21.720 --> 33:22.790
Let me ask first.

33:28.790 --> 33:29.440
Fang.

33:29.470 --> 33:30.250
What are you doing here?

33:30.270 --> 33:30.920
Go sit down.

33:30.960 --> 33:32.320
It's okay, Senior He. I'll help you.

33:32.590 --> 33:33.830
We can't have guests cooking for us.

33:33.830 --> 33:34.200
Really, it's fine.

33:34.200 --> 33:35.850
Go get some drinks from the fridge for them.

33:35.880 --> 33:36.640
Hurry, go on.

33:36.880 --> 33:37.640
Alright then.

33:39.550 --> 33:40.110
Suye.

33:42.110 --> 33:43.720
Manager Xu from the hotel.

33:43.720 --> 33:44.590
You remember her, right?

33:44.990 --> 33:46.320
She says she's nearby.

33:46.580 --> 33:47.420
She wants to come over.

33:49.480 --> 33:50.480
Is she alone?

33:52.110 --> 33:53.580
She might be with Manager Shen.

34:00.070 --> 34:00.640
Should I...

34:00.640 --> 34:02.720
It's fine, just tell them to come over together.

34:03.740 --> 34:05.680
Okay, I'll reply to them then.

34:05.680 --> 34:06.210
Go ahead.

34:20.380 --> 34:21.659
Go up that way.

34:21.760 --> 34:22.760
How do I get there?

34:23.969 --> 34:24.860
You lead the way.

34:26.699 --> 34:27.610
Would you like a drink?

34:27.639 --> 34:28.290
Yes.

34:40.760 --> 34:42.360
We're out of the elevator now.

34:43.150 --> 34:44.440
Xiangya, I haven't figure out

34:44.440 --> 34:45.110
how to put it yet.

34:45.110 --> 34:45.760
Let's forget it.

34:46.420 --> 34:47.750
We're already here.

34:48.210 --> 34:49.250
But I really...

35:07.960 --> 35:08.730
Please come in.

35:16.550 --> 35:18.100
I've put the slippers here for you.

35:18.120 --> 35:19.950
Put on the slippers and sit with them for a while.

35:20.320 --> 35:21.230
I'll go prepare the meal.

35:23.480 --> 35:24.030
Please, have a seat.

35:24.480 --> 35:25.230
This game!

35:25.230 --> 35:26.400
I'm really good at this.

35:26.400 --> 35:27.030
You can play this?

35:27.030 --> 35:27.960
I can't get past this part. You try.

35:27.960 --> 35:29.190
Let's play together.

35:54.230 --> 35:55.630
Here it comes.

35:56.900 --> 35:58.420
Perilla cucumber carrot soup.

36:00.280 --> 36:00.960
Looks impressive.

36:00.960 --> 36:01.440
The main event.

36:01.440 --> 36:02.300
It looks so delicious.

36:02.320 --> 36:03.680
It's good for dispelling cold. Try some.

36:03.710 --> 36:05.360
Have a bowl.

36:05.360 --> 36:06.400
Is it for cooling down or warming up?

36:06.400 --> 36:07.320
Warming up.

36:07.320 --> 36:07.960
Okay.

36:07.960 --> 36:08.360
I'll try some of that lotus root.

36:08.360 --> 36:08.800
Be careful, it's hot.

36:08.800 --> 36:09.630
Is it good?

36:09.630 --> 36:10.670
Is it tasty?

36:10.670 --> 36:11.320
Mm, it's delicious.

36:11.320 --> 36:11.880
He wants some too.

36:11.880 --> 36:12.670
Have some more soup.

36:12.670 --> 36:13.450
That's enough, that's enough.

36:13.470 --> 36:14.280
Here you go.

36:14.440 --> 36:15.000
Thank you.

36:15.000 --> 36:15.940
Is this shredded potato or...

36:15.970 --> 36:16.700
I don't know.

36:16.720 --> 36:17.000
I want one too.

36:17.030 --> 36:17.630
Is it good?

36:18.260 --> 36:18.780
How is it?

36:19.150 --> 36:19.550
It's good, right?

36:19.550 --> 36:20.590
It tastes so healthy.

36:21.000 --> 36:21.510
It's incredibly delicious.

36:21.880 --> 36:22.280
Tasty, isn't it?

36:22.280 --> 36:23.150
Tissue, tissue, tissue!

36:23.150 --> 36:23.840
What happened?

36:24.920 --> 36:25.480
Wipe it off.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.360
Thanks.

36:28.000 --> 36:30.440
If the tissue doesn't clean it completely,

36:30.510 --> 36:31.990
do you want to try a stain removal pen?

36:33.910 --> 36:34.800
It's delicious.

36:34.800 --> 36:36.320
There's one next to the washing machine in the storage room.

36:36.320 --> 36:37.120
Okay.

36:37.150 --> 36:38.000
I'm sorry.

36:38.000 --> 36:38.710
I'll go get it then.

36:40.720 --> 36:41.890
The radish flavour is strong.

36:46.600 --> 36:47.840
It's really tasty.

36:49.140 --> 36:50.020
Senior He,

36:50.850 --> 36:52.130
do you have any chili sauce?

36:52.200 --> 36:53.070
Personally,

36:53.070 --> 36:53.480
Yes, I do.

36:53.480 --> 36:54.320
I'd like to improve it a bit.

36:54.320 --> 36:54.670
I think it's at...

36:54.670 --> 36:55.550
I'll go get it.

36:55.660 --> 36:56.570
The flavour is a bit mild.

36:56.600 --> 36:57.640
I'd like to make it a bit stronger.

36:57.670 --> 36:58.480
What do you want to add?

37:21.280 --> 37:22.440
Manager Shen.

37:24.110 --> 37:27.150
Senior He used to have a girlfriend.

37:27.150 --> 37:28.060
Have you heard about it?

37:34.670 --> 37:36.150
I haven't heard about that.

37:36.590 --> 37:39.030
They were college classmates.

37:39.800 --> 37:41.000
They dated for about...

37:41.550 --> 37:43.070
about five or six years, I think.

37:43.540 --> 37:44.850
Eventually, it was because

37:44.960 --> 37:47.920
the girlfriend got an opportunity to study abroad.

37:48.860 --> 37:50.530
So she broke up with Senior He.

37:51.360 --> 37:53.550
And after she left, she never came back.

37:55.960 --> 37:56.670
What's wrong?

37:57.050 --> 37:59.530
Do you also think I shouldn't go study abroad?

38:00.230 --> 38:00.920
No, that's not it.

38:01.560 --> 38:03.690
I just suddenly thought of a friend of mine.

38:04.240 --> 38:05.510
She also went abroad to study.

38:07.760 --> 38:09.960
Senior He was depressed for a long time because of that.

38:14.240 --> 38:16.050
So, you...

38:25.030 --> 38:25.960
I want to say...

38:28.020 --> 38:29.730
If you really don't like him,

38:30.310 --> 38:31.480
stop leading him on.

38:33.280 --> 38:35.030
Ever since you rejected Senior He,

38:35.510 --> 38:36.320
he's been in low spirits

38:36.320 --> 38:37.320
and preoccupied with worries.

38:38.030 --> 38:39.800
Today you even came to his house.

38:40.710 --> 38:41.710
Do you want to see

38:41.730 --> 38:44.040
how upset and heartbroken he is because of you?

38:44.590 --> 38:46.230
Or are you trying to prove how charming you are?

38:47.400 --> 38:49.320
Senior He has always been a gentle

38:49.320 --> 38:50.300
and kind person.

38:50.710 --> 38:51.360
But that doesn't mean

38:51.360 --> 38:53.150
you can treat him so casually.

38:54.910 --> 38:56.580
If you really don't like him,

38:57.670 --> 38:59.230
please stop bothering him.

39:09.150 --> 39:11.880
The situation between He Suye and me

39:13.980 --> 39:15.390
might be a bit complicated.

39:19.400 --> 39:20.710
But you're right.

39:24.430 --> 39:25.950
I held him back.

39:34.760 --> 39:35.950
Thank you for reminding me.

41:32.820 --> 41:33.650
The elevator is here.

41:33.870 --> 41:34.790
Be careful on your way.

41:35.150 --> 41:35.670
Goodbye, Senior He.

41:35.670 --> 41:36.670
Goodbye, Senior He.

41:37.550 --> 41:38.190
Goodbye.

41:39.710 --> 41:40.630
Fang.

41:41.320 --> 41:42.000
Could you stay for a moment?

41:42.030 --> 41:42.950
I have something to tell you.

41:44.130 --> 41:45.250
You guys go ahead, it's fine.

41:48.190 --> 41:48.550
Goodbye.

41:48.570 --> 41:49.310
Goodbye, goodbye.

41:59.360 --> 42:00.280
Senior He,

42:01.110 --> 42:01.920
I'm sorry.

42:04.760 --> 42:05.670
Xiao Fang.

42:06.840 --> 42:07.840
I was told

42:08.230 --> 42:10.880
by my grandfather to supervise your internship.

42:12.160 --> 42:13.410
You are my student,

42:14.710 --> 42:15.400
but,

42:16.090 --> 42:17.490
you're also just my student.

42:30.390 --> 42:31.620
Next semester,

42:32.030 --> 42:34.590
you won't need to intern under me anymore.

42:36.440 --> 42:37.900
You are an excellent student,

42:38.460 --> 42:40.420
very diligent and intelligent.

42:41.280 --> 42:42.240
I believe

42:42.400 --> 42:44.400
you will definitely achieve great things in your studies.

42:49.810 --> 42:51.160
You don't need to rush to answer now.

42:51.470 --> 42:53.510
Think it over when you get back.

42:55.220 --> 42:56.860
Be careful on your way home.

42:59.000 --> 42:59.800
I'll be going now.

43:35.710 --> 43:36.920
When you went downstairs just now,

43:37.310 --> 43:38.710
did you catch up with Xifan?

43:40.440 --> 43:41.050
No.

43:42.730 --> 43:45.650
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have brought her.

43:47.800 --> 43:48.590
It's not your fault.

43:50.480 --> 43:52.160
Did she tell you what's on her mind?

43:53.070 --> 43:54.070
What do you mean?

43:57.760 --> 43:59.830
She's been in a lot of pain since she rejected you.

44:00.320 --> 44:01.230
She's been very conflicted.

44:01.230 --> 44:02.440
Conflicted for days.

44:04.150 --> 44:05.880
The reason for her conflict

44:06.670 --> 44:08.230
is because she cares about you.

44:10.230 --> 44:11.760
She's afraid of rushing into a relationship with you,

44:11.760 --> 44:13.230
and then immediately being in different countries.

44:13.670 --> 44:14.440
If conflicts arise,

44:14.440 --> 44:15.880
there won't even be a chance to communicate.

44:16.610 --> 44:18.530
In the end, you might not even be able to remain friends.

44:25.370 --> 44:26.390
These words,

44:30.230 --> 44:31.630
why doesn't she say them herself?

44:32.880 --> 44:35.190
Actually, Xifan's romantic experiences

44:35.510 --> 44:36.490
are very limited.

44:37.670 --> 44:40.230
She only had one first love that lasted seven years.

44:40.550 --> 44:41.630
They broke up just last year.

44:42.360 --> 44:43.800
They were in a long-distance relationship for a long time.

44:44.550 --> 44:47.190
During the last period, she was in a really bad state.

44:48.710 --> 44:50.750
She's very afraid of getting hurt again.

45:16.760 --> 45:17.840
Later, it was because

45:17.840 --> 45:20.510
the girlfriend got an opportunity to study abroad,

45:20.880 --> 45:22.760
so she broke up with Senior He.

45:23.320 --> 45:25.510
And after she left, she never came back.

45:27.070 --> 45:28.240
I love you too much.

45:28.640 --> 45:30.640
That's why I didn't realize you've always been so selfish.

45:31.550 --> 45:32.430
You studying abroad

45:32.430 --> 45:34.190
will cause so much trouble for those around you.

45:34.760 --> 45:36.780
How come I'm only realising how selfish you are now?

45:37.880 --> 45:39.800
Senior He has always been a very gentle

45:39.800 --> 45:40.880
and kind person.

45:41.280 --> 45:41.960
But that doesn't mean

45:41.960 --> 45:43.630
you can treat him so casually.
